    "This reduces producers' requirements and improves communication flexibility.",
    "Meanwhile, DCP supports many types of producers and consumers, including UPF, service data plane function, network exposure function (NEF), RAN, application function (AF), data storage function, and AI models.",
    "It also enables simultaneous real-time stream data processing and peak-clipping processing, which pronounces an improvement compared with current SBI, DU session, message queuing telemetry transport, and Kafka.",
    "With good flexibility, DCP can be deployed as an independent NF or colocated with existing NFs.",
    "Fig. 17 shows an example of DCP in an AI task: multi-task face recognition."
